f=Executive Office/vista/marketplace/north-star-metric/SKILL.md · tx=<!-- Unmodified copy "north-star-metric" skill, selected fulfill catalog's "vyon-north-star-metrics" slot vista. Chosen over phuryn/pm-skills' north-star-metric (22k★) because version carries half catalog entry actually requires: anti-metrics counter-metrics explicit thresholds catalog's guardrails each; alert thresholds"), plus metric_tree_builder.py rendering tool. phuryn version defines NSM inputs only. catalog entry's remaining elements "confirm NSM venture" "monthly review marcus" workflow cadence, metric methodology, live vista's operational/ layer (commands skill routing) built. NOTE: source's Integration Points table references home repo's skills (brainstorm-okrs, outcome-roadmap, etc.). Kept verbatim; system equivalents are: brainstorm-okrs marcus/okr-cascade; prioritization-frameworks vista/rice-prioritization; OKR verification vista/okr-quality-checker. Script tested 2026-07-06: `--demo --format markdown` `--format mermaid` run clean (stdlib only, dependencies). --> · h2:Overview=North Star Metric (NSM) single number best represents value your product delivers customers. Sean Ellis popularized framing; Amplitude codified playbook; Lean Analytics calls related concept "One Metric Matters" (OMTM). NSM **one** number, dashboard. job align entire team engineering, marketing, sales, support shared definition "we won quarter." skill produces complete NSM specification: NSM itself, 3-5 **input metrics** team directly influence, **leading indicators** move days weeks before inputs, **anti-metrics** (things move wrong direction), **counter-metrics** guard against gaming. Python tool (`metric_tree_builder.py`) emits spec JSON, Markdown, Mermaid tree diagram README Confluence page. first artifact team produce after defining strategy before writing OKRs. Once NSM set, OKRs map directly moving input metrics, roadmaps justify themselves which input metric they target. · h2:Core Capabilities=**NSM selection** score candidates against five tests (customer value, strategic alignment, leading, single number, movable) five Amplitude archetypes., **Metric-tree decomposition** break NSM 3-5 input metrics explicit formula (multiplicative additive funnel ratio)., **Leading indicators** assign 2-3 input move before input (the daily/weekly dashboard)., **Guardrails** anti-metrics (protect customer) counter-metrics (protect business), explicit thresholds., **Rendering** Mermaid tree, JSON dashboard config, Markdown Python tool. · wu=**New product strategic direction** before OKRs roadmap, define NSM inputs., **Strategic re-alignment** dashboard metrics one knows which optimize., **Cross-functional friction** marketing, product, growth disagree what "success" means., **Investor board reporting** NSM becomes headline metric., **A/B experimentation guardrails** test reports NSM impact plus counter-metric impact. · wu=**When use:** early-stage discovery (use `discovery/` first you don't know what value you deliver); pure infrastructure work indirect user-value chain; before org aligned strategy (the NSM exposes disagreement resolve it). · h2:Clarify First=Before defining NSM, confirm inputs. any unknown vague, ASK assume: · h2:Clarify First=**Core customer value product delivers** drives NSM candidate selection; NSM proxy this, revenue lagging metric, **Business archetype** attention transaction productivity marketplace engagement sets Amplitude archetype input-metric formula (multiplicative/additive/funnel/ratio), **Input metrics team directly influence** 3-5 nodes tree; team can't move them, tree decoration, **Anti-/counter-metrics guard** thresholds protect customer business against gamed NSM · h2:Clarify First=Stop rule: ask 2-3 change output. user says "just draft it," proceed list your assumptions top artifact. · h2:Quick Start=`python scripts/metric_tree_builder.py --input nsm_spec.json --format mermaid   # render the metric tree \· python scripts/metric_tree_builder.py --demo --format markdown                 # worked SaaS productivity NSM` · h2:References=Load reference matches task keep file lean pull detail demand: · h2:References=**[references/nsm-playbook.md](references/nsm-playbook.md)** five quality tests, Amplitude archetypes real company examples, metric-tree structure input math, leading indicators, anti-/counter-metrics thresholds, step-by-step workflow, `metric_tree_builder.py` reference (flags, input JSON, Mermaid sample), troubleshooting, success criteria. Read selecting NSM building tree., **[references/nsm-framework-guide.md](references/nsm-framework-guide.md)** deep dive three overlapping frameworks (Sean Ellis NSM, Amplitude NSM, Lean Analytics OMTM), input-metric math, worked examples across five business archetypes. Read comparing frameworks working specific archetype., **[references/red-flags.md](references/red-flags.md)** concrete examples NSM specs wrong, they're bad, fix them. Read reviewing NSM diagnosing gamed/lagging metric., **assets/nsm_spec_template.md** fill-in template NSM specification matching tool's JSON shape. Use drafting spec. · h2:Scope & Limitations=**In Scope:** NSM selection across archetypes; input-metric tree decomposition explicit math; leading-indicator selection input; anti-/counter-metric definition thresholds; Python rendering tool; handoff OKR drafting roadmap prioritization. **Out Scope:** building actual analytics dashboards (BI tools produces spec); statistical experiment design (`discovery/brainstorm-experiments/`); financial/revenue forecasting (`finance/`); OKR drafting (`brainstorm-okrs/`); data quality validation (`data-analytics/`). **Caveats:** NSM exposes strategic disagreement resolve escalate strategy decision, metric debate. Pure financial outputs (revenue, ARR) usually lagging; pick customer-value proxy revenue follows from. NSM aligns; teams still need component metrics diagnostics. team without instrumentation cannot operate against NSM spend telemetry first. · h2:Integration Points=\| Integration \| Direction \| Description \| · h2:Integration Points=\|-------------\|-----------\|-------------\| · h2:Integration Points=\| `discovery/brainstorm-ideas/` \| Receives from \| Opportunity discovery defines what value to deliver; NSM measures it \| · h2:Integration Points=\| `discovery/identify-assumptions/` \| Receives from \| NSM candidates surface assumptions about what customers value \| · h2:Integration Points=\| `execution/brainstorm-okrs/` \| Feeds into \| NSM becomes the quarterly Objective; inputs become Key Results \| · h2:Integration Points=\| `execution/outcome-roadmap/` \| Feeds into \| Roadmap items justify themselves by which input metric they target \| · h2:Integration Points=\| `execution/prioritization-frameworks/` \| Pairs with \| NSM impact is one of the scoring criteria (e.g., RICE Impact, Weighted) \| · h2:Integration Points=\| `execution/status-update-generator/` \| Feeds into \| NSM and input movements feature in Highlights of weekly updates \| · h2:Integration Points=\| `data-analytics/` (domain) \| Pairs with \| NSM spec becomes the schema for dashboards and event taxonomies \| · h2:Integration Points=\| `executive-reporting/` (senior-pm) \| Feeds into \| Monthly board packets lead with NSM trend \|